Package gobblin.source.extractor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CheckpointableWatermark
    Watermark that is Comparable and Checkpointable
    ComparableWatermark
    Watermark that is also Comparable.
    Extractor<S,D>
    An interface for classes that are responsible for extracting data from a data source.
    StreamingExtractor<S,D>
    An interface for implementing streaming / continuous extractors
    Watermark
    A Watermark represents a checkpoint in data processing, and indicates that all data up to specific point has been pulled from some source.
